sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant RPCHandler
    participant SQLConverter
    participant SQLParser
    participant SQLValidator
    participant Mempool
    participant POPConsensus
    participant P2PNetwork
    participant Ledger
    participant TableSync
    participant Database

    Client->>RPCHandler: sql_submit({sql, account})
    RPCHandler->>SQLConverter: to_transaction(sql, account, tx_type)
    SQLConverter->>SQLParser: parse(sql)
    SQLParser-->>SQLConverter: ParsedSQL
    SQLConverter->>SQLValidator: validate(parsed, registry)
    SQLValidator-->>SQLConverter: valid=True
    SQLConverter-->>RPCHandler: Transaction
    RPCHandler->>Mempool: add(transaction)
    RPCHandler-->>Client: {tx_hash, status: "queued"}

    Note over POPConsensus: Leader 定时触发共识
    POPConsensus->>Mempool: get_all()
    POPConsensus->>POPConsensus: build_proposal(transactions)
    POPConsensus->>P2PNetwork: broadcast(PROPOSAL)

    Note over POPConsensus: 交易集共识
    P2PNetwork-->>POPConsensus: votes collected (>2/3)
    POPConsensus->>POPConsensus: build_block(consensus_tx_set)
    POPConsensus->>P2PNetwork: broadcast(NEW_BLOCK)

    P2PNetwork-->>POPConsensus: block votes (>2/3)
    POPConsensus->>Ledger: append_block(block)

    Note over TableSync: 监听新区块
    Ledger-->>TableSync: on_new_block(block)
    TableSync->>Database: execute(sql_from_transaction)
    TableSync->>TableSync: update_sync_height()
